definitions.definition: To offer for acceptance ; to propose to give ; to make a tender of.
examples: to proffer friendship, a gift, or services

definitions.definition: To attempt or essay of one's own accord ; to undertake or propose to undertake.

main_definition: ( transitive , reflexive ) To offer for acceptance ; to propose to give ; to make a tender of.
secondary_definitions: ( transitive , obsolete ) To attempt or essay of one's own accord ; to undertake or propose to undertake.
